Titolo: Plundered Hearts

Anno: 1987

Descrizione: Plundered Hearts is an interactive fiction video game created by Amy Briggs and published by Infocom in 1987. Infocom's only game in the romance genre, it was released simultaneously for the Commodore 64, Atari 8-bit family, Atari ST, Amiga, Macintosh, and IBM PC compatibles. It is Infocom's twenty-eighth game.